Package: gppm
Version: 0.3.0
Title: Gaussian Process Panel Modeling
Description: Provides an implementation of Gaussian process panel
        modeling (GPPM). GPPM is described in Karch, Brandmaier &
        Voelkle (2020; <DOI:10.3389/fpsyg.2020.00351>) and Karch (2016;
        <DOI:10.18452/17641>). Essentially, GPPM is Gaussian process
        based modeling of longitudinal panel data. 'gppm' also supports
        regular Gaussian process regression (with a focus on flexible
        model specification), and multi-task learning.
